data.description: Stunning Single Family Home in Desirable Oakland Park, 3 bedroom, 2 bath. This lovely home features; 42 inch Shaker White Kitchen Cabinetry, Granite Counter-tops, Stainless Steel Appliances, tile flooring throughout, carport, newer AC, large bedrooms, open floor plan, fresh paint in and out, Farm doors and upgraded doors throughout the home. Both bathrooms are completely remodeled and impact doors and windows. With a spacious backyard to fit a pool.
